705703f-a.text:
749.763 Metropolitan Ave., north side, east from Graham Ave., Also seen is 346-354 Graham Ave., at the N.E. corner of Metropolitan Ave. The frame building at the corner, was erected in 1883 and is still standing.
March 3, 1935.
P. L Sperr.

704672f-a.text:
236-242 Graham Ave., east side, from 236 at extreme right, to Metropolitan Ave. At the corner, is seen the 14th Street Canarsie B.M.T. Subway Station.
March 3, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
